# .spec/ is mostly regenerable/runtime for consumer projects. Track only the
# authored governance dir (.spec/memory/ — constitution, decisions, hooks);
# ignore .spec/templates + .spec/scripts (regenerable from root source) and
# .spec/agents.json (runtime, churns on every agents add/remove).
